  "text": "The study was approved by the institutional research commission of the Swiss Tropical and Public Health Institute (Basel, Switzerland). Ethical clearance was obtained from the Ethics Committee of the Ministry of Health and Social Welfare, Zanzibar (reference no. 16) [CITATION_1] . All participants in this study gave written informed consent, which was provided by the parent or guardian for the children involved. Additionally, children provided oral assent.",
